source.name: Community Project Fund Allocations (CPF) - Appropriated:2009-10 Allocated:2009-10
source.description:
Listing of member allocations of money to Community Projects. Monies may be allocated from appropriations in the current year and/or re-allocated from an unspent appropriation in a previous year. Information relating to the recipient, amount and allocating authority are included in the Community Project Fund. The report is issued by the Senate Finance Office and is available as both a .csv file and it's original PDF format.

The Report includes fields for the recipient project's title, address, city, state, zip code, phone number, contact person, county and funding amount by year as well as the disbursing Senator, the Senator's affiliation with the Majority or Minority, the Agency Code of the recipient project and a description of the recipient project.
